# CLI Module
#
# Command-line interface implementation for the Simple compiler.
# Handles argument parsing, command dispatch, and user interaction.
#
# Public API:
#   - use app.cli.main.{cli_main, handle_command}
#   - use app.cli.args.{parse_args, CliArgs}

